div1.p:
(They were produced in court and deposed to by
Elizabeth Robinson
) When he dropped them, I said, I see what you have been about, but you shall not go; then he rushed towards me and knocked the candle out of my hand; and we had a struggle upon the stairs. Mr. Sligh came out; we found that there was another man in Mr. Robinson's room, my wife saw that man make off, she called out to me and I pursued him. I did lay hold of him, but he struggled and got from me. Mr. Sligh took the prisoner. I am certain he is the person I saw in Mr. Robinson's room.

Allpress. Yes. (A hanger produced by
John Dinmore
).
